{"tid":529061,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【劏場翻生】黎婆婆賣樓買劏舖 收舖後稱:「慘過雷曼」","createTime":"2018-01-14T13:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T11:04:45.000Z","uid":17738,"like":4,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"2c1db0009977f40b3f4198416f640f51062639ae","tid":529061,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180114/large/1515921403_6e6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F1515921403_6e6b.jpg&h=5711086a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180114/large/1515921378_5e39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F1515921378_5e39.jpg&h=952ddecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎婆婆(中)與女兒(右)憶述多年前賣樓買劏舖。<br />\n<br />\n今年地皇廣場近七成業主團結招租，劏場有返啲旺氣，業主黎婆婆倍感欣慰。<br />\n<br />\n她憶述:「當初賣咗自己層樓，睇緊樓，諗住買另一層樓來收租。點知個經紀就show左呢度(地皇廣場)，話參觀下啦，睇下啲舖位。一來到就一班人哄哄哄，個女被人哄左另一邊，售價410萬元，仲以為300幾呎，咁買舖著數過買樓啦。點知得30幾呎，個陣話睇左位先，點知阿女已經落咗訂金。」<br />\n<br />\n阿女在旁補充:「個陣樓市熾熱，買住宅被人反價。個經紀sell我地呢度好有前景，話會打造主題商場，如先達廣場。又話呢度係會幫我地搞好個商場先俾返我地，心諗只係收租。首2年有5厘回報。又話有300萬元宣傳費用。收樓後嚇一跳，連入口係邊都唔知。」<br />\n黎婆婆接著說:「收舖先知咁慘，首2年5厘回報，係幾筍，仲諗住收返後加租，點知返到來，十室九空!暈得一陣，無從投訴，仲慘過雷曼。」她坦言有被騙感覺，經過幾年奮鬥，業主們團結搞返旺個場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180114/57706953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57706953&d=n17qn7TJDXoHaR3Der2I%2FL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7e137851\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57706953&h=f71592a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180114/57706953</a>"},{"pid":"661d940ea6fa57a4fd20ba112552500102ca633b","tid":529061,"uid":22700,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:10:51.000Z","msg":"賺硬架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a88aa35acfbeb8b25872b312298ef3ea07c4a4","tid":529061,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"地皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fde78d98c8f9e73eee48767c1adf54737640e60","tid":529061,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"升到600萬 你地仲笑唔笑得出"},{"pid":"36fea896a80a3c45dcf937d85ac2880a852dc99b","tid":529061,"uid":81113,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:12:59.000Z","msg":"低能<br />\n比曬錢先知響邊度<br />\n去街巿買菜啦<br />\n抵佢比人呃"},{"pid":"3f35ee9b9be57062d3a05dab99b8b6a3c8611be9","tid":529061,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"【劏場翻生】荃灣地皇廣場逾十舖獲零食店洽租<br />\n業主：曙光！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180114/large/1515920850_432c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F1515920850_432c.jpg&h=f8c52ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣地皇廣場2樓逾10個舖獲零食店洽租，有望翻身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180114/large/1515920861_e6fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F1515920861_e6fa.jpg&h=6bb00e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該場業委會委員王榮梅表示，自1樓租予食肆後，該場人流旺咗!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180114/large/1515920877_3d97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F1515920877_3d97.jpg&h=45120546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地皇廣場1樓大部份樓面聯合租予食肆後，暫時搞返旺呢一層。<br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n本港著名劏場之一荃灣地皇廣場自1樓大部份樓面聯合出租予食肆後，人流及租賃情況略為改善。<br />\n地皇廣場業委會委員王榮梅表示，原本1樓多個舖位聯合出租予百貨店，無奈當時零售不景氣，租不成，後來轉租予食肆，結果開到成巷成市。自1樓變身美食廣場後，人流增加6至7成。7成業主加入聯租，該場目前整體出租率達80%。舖位是劏舖，實用33至40方呎，月租最平約3000元。<br />\n人流好轉，有零食店主動洽租，擬承租2樓14至15個面積約三、四十方呎舖位出租，面積共約500至600方呎，好想佢可以入到來。佢地有意租3至5年。<br />\n她稱:「租客搵到食，個場先搞到落去。香港好多劏舖，係我地口中既死場。我哋希望成為香港一個&hellip;&hellip;唔好話代表，只要攞出香港精神，劏場有曙光。」<br />\n劏場人流好轉，她憶述聯租過程困難:「劏場最大問題係業權好散，一定要經過呢一條路(聯租)，個舖太細啦，必須打通。幾乎逐個業主解釋，過程遇到拒絕，唔好聽既說話，例如你搞咁多嘢做咩？係咪係度搵著數呀！」為何要搞聯租，她話:「見到個場毫無起色，與其等死，不如團結啲。」<br />\n她持有該場1樓1個舖位，係當年老公買來送俾佢，實用41方呎，目前每月收租約5000元，回報率約1.25厘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180114/57706902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57706902&d=n17qn7TJDXoHaR3Der2I%2FL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=082d23b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57706902&h=87497abd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180114/57706902</a>"},{"pid":"f1b3434f4cfc5d1d951ab415eac0e432a1e10759","tid":529061,"uid":62815,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n明明開吉野家同霸王山莊咪好地地<br />\n開埋d咁ge19場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90990db2930f47043544b7403fb2b85f10ab860d","tid":529061,"uid":81113,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回報約1.25厘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n銀行做定期都多過你"},{"pid":"618d16bc1c006e116802b386a347eb95dd5688d8","tid":529061,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"【劏場翻生】4000蚊租舖賣茶葉 營業額近2萬元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180114/large/1515923905_d9f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F1515923905_d9f2.jpg&h=28d4304b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁生原本經朋友介紹到1樓某食肆做廚師，見到個場旺返，即刻以月租4000元租間舖，賣茶葉，由太太看住茶葉舖，自己就係隔離幫人打工。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣地皇廣場翻生，租客袁先生現在於1樓某食肆做廚師，「朋友介紹來打工，咁就知道有呢個場。以前係深水埗都有賣茶葉，見到呢度人流好，租又平，純粹玩下，本身有職業，希望介紹啲靚茶俾茶友認識下。」他補充：「咁嘅租，應該係有回報!」<br />\n<br />\n租約期2年，投資額近廿萬元，開業4個多月，袁生坦言：「夠交租，夠俾人工，營業額萬幾兩萬蚊。而家人流一路增加，比之前好咗好多，暑假剛開業時，好少人㗎咋，一日都無二、三十，而家閒日最少800人。單係隔離，我幫另一個老闆做食肆，一日都賣400個飯盒，仲未計其他人呢！」<br />\n他睇好該場的發展，已準備承租1樓某個舖位，自己搞食肆，月租2萬多元，預計今年3月開業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180114/57707099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57707099&d=n17qn7TJDXoHaR3Der2I%2FL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d97c7662\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57707099&h=dc20c5b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180114/57707099</a>"},{"pid":"abe86fe08d2c97243f389c9d570c4254ba046ddb","tid":529061,"uid":90601,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"無記錯當年係信和開始玩劏鋪先<br />\n好多賣後生仔野既「據聞」好搵得<br />\n就爆左其他劏場出黎 結果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班友唔思考信和做得起 唔係因為信和<br />\n而係因為信和係旺角正中心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef31da8c433c59785142b99cc181f381c16a2299","tid":529061,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"【劏場翻生】街坊：1樓食肆吸引，有興趣返來!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180114/large/1515922956_eda3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F1515922956_eda3.jpg&h=9a7a1c16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣街坊陳先生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180114/large/1515922889_4aa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F1515922889_4aa8.jpg&h=b178b766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣街坊馮先生<br />\n<br />\n荃灣劏場地皇廣場有起色，街坊馮先生表示：「商場好咗，知道之前係死場，又話八成未租出，估唔到而家咁多舖頭租得出。有興趣返來嘅，個食肆囉！如果再開多啲舖頭會返來多啲。」<br />\n<br />\n荃灣街坊陳先生表示：「地皇廣場之前都唔係咁多人流，好多舖位都是租唔出，以前二、三樓吉舖比較多，1樓而家有嘢食，多咗人，暫時都幾吸引，好似仿照其他商場。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180114/57707053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57707053&d=n17qn7TJDXoHaR3Der2I%2FL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3aa3f412\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F57707053&h=766dc8d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180114/57707053</a>"},{"pid":"cab7b0c565ed8bbb6b26be327a399337571ff5c3","tid":529061,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"個門口細到on9"},{"pid":"5e1b0a10ce0c3617dc82c8618f29e251f55678f2","tid":529061,"uid":52946,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:24:00.000Z","msg":"個經紀sell我地呢度好有前景，話會打造主題商場<br />\n信班SELL狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7418a54f7a5fb7b4cc440c250ae8d7a36a318ee4","tid":529061,"uid":17738,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"全香港99%劏場都係輸錢嘅，基本上打莊贏晒，仲要睇管理處條款，專呃c9，阿婆，強國人"},{"pid":"fcba9a26a58d8226d641de3eb529ecb0062dffb2","tid":529061,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"死場之霸首都去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/n